A comprehensive covid-19 dataframe

Source: R/updateCovid.R
updateCovid.Rd

This function gives back a dataframe of total cases, total deaths, and total recoveres from covid-19 in the world.

updateCovid()

Value

A dataframe containing the cumulative daily cases, deaths, and recovers of covid-19 of all countries.

Author

Ali Malek

Examples

updateCovid()
